Posts.Content: On Mar 18, 2019 5:23 PM pwierz107 wrote: I've been taking letrazole and Prolia for about two years now.  Having the usual joint pain with letrazole, but I was wondering if anyone out there has had side effects from the Prolia.  I've had terrible itching of my arms for two years now.  My oncologist is of no help.  I've taken Prolia for a year and I haven't noticed any side effects.
